HOw we auto update data in Power BI report

we update daet on report and report will auto reflect on it.
data integrity and data cleaniness is important to not to tamper reports.
Process is same in both power bi and tableau , i did on power bi, first click on reprot, we can also see dataset along side it.
We have otion of action in which we we see refresh file, but it denies due to gateway error.
we have to download gateway in gateway connection option
that gateway establish connection in dataset stored in local or cloud with power BI service.
after setting up gateway, click on refresh button on main report to check changes.
we can setup auto refresh at given time inb settings
